Class OpenIGTConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • InputOutput.OpenIGTConnection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.medcare.igtl.network.IOpenIgtPacketListener

    public class OpenIGTConnection
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.medcare.igtl.network.IOpenIgtPacketListener
    This class is for a connection based on OpenIGTLink. As a prerequisite MITK v2016.11 has to run in the background. The connection is established by using the online stream.
    Author:
    team3
